name: android-navigation-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for navigation and app structure in Android
globs: **/*.{kt,xml}

- Use Jetpack Navigation for fragment navigation
- Implement proper deep linking
- Handle navigation state persisting through process death
- Use proper intent filters for external navigation
- Implement proper back navigation
- Handle orientation changes correctly
- Use Single Activity architecture when possible
- Implement navigation animations
- Handle task stack appropriately
- Create proper navigation graphs
- Use SafeArgs for type-safe navigation 